ekaw#Event: The conferencebanquet and the scientificevent are both parented by the scientificevent.
ekaw#Person: pcmember and scmember are parents of students and paperauthors. They are also parents of agency staff and conferenceparticipant. ocmember and conferenceparticipant are both parents of conferenceparticipant.
ekaw#Accepted_Paper: Acceptedpaper is the child of evaluatedpaper and the parent of rejectedpaper.
ekaw#Rejected_Paper: The rejected paper is the child of evaluatedpaper and assignedpaper. The submittedpaper is the child of posterpaper.
ekaw#Evaluated_Paper: The assignedpaper is the child of submittedpaper and evaluatedpaper. The rejectedpaper is the child of acceptedpaper and the evaluatedpaper is the child of assignedpaper.
ekaw#Camera_Ready_Paper: camerareadypaper is a child of paper which is the parent of a website.
ekaw#Positive_Review: The positivereview is the child of the review and the parent of the negativereview.
ekaw#Workshop_Paper: The workshoppaper is a child of paper which is the parent of the demopaper.
ekaw#Industrial_Paper: Industrialpaper is the child of paper and is the parent of posterpaper.
ekaw#Paper: Paper is the parent of both regularpaper and posterpaper. It is also the parent of both abstract and tutorial abstract.
ekaw#Conference_Paper: The conference paper is a child of the document which is the parent of the website.
ekaw#Industrial_Session: Industrialsession is child of conferencesession and scientificevent. Individualpresentation and invitedtalk are both parented by scientificevent.
ekaw#Conference_Session: The conferencesession is the parent of the industrialsession and the postersession.
ekaw#Regular_Session: The regularsession is the child of the session and the parent of the demosession.
ekaw#Poster_Session: The postersession is child of the scientificevent which is parented by the contributedtalk and the individualpresentation.
ekaw#Demo_Session: The demosession is the child of the session and the parent of the regularsession.
ekaw#Session: The session is the parent of the regularsession and the demosession. It is also the parent of the conference and the postersession.
ekaw#Abstract: The abstract is a child of the website and the document invitedtalkabstract. It is also the parent of tutorialabstract.
ekaw#Document: The multiauthor volume is the parent of the proceedings, the conferenceproceedings and the flyer. The paper is the parent of the programme brochure and the review is the parent of the positive review.
ekaw#Paper_Author: The paperauthor is the child of the person who is the parent of possiblereviewer and pcmember.
ekaw#Conference_Trip: conferencetrip is a child of socialvent which is a child of an event.
ekaw#Social_Event: Socialvent is the parent of conferencetrip and conferencebanquet. It is also the child of scientificevent and socialvent.
ekaw#Tutorial_Abstract: The abstract of a tutorial is the child of a document which is parented by a programmebrochure.
ekaw#Conference_Participant: The conferenceparticipant is the parent of ocmember, occhair and demochair. The child of pcmember and sessionchair is also the parent of pcmember and pcmember. The student is also the parent of the conferenceparticipant.
ekaw#Submitted_Paper: The parent of submittedpaper is assignedpaper, the parent of evaluatedpaper and the parent of rejectedpaper. Paper is also the parent of camerareadypaper.
ekaw#Assigned_Paper: The assignedpaper is the child of both submittedpaper and acceptedpaper. It is the parent of both workshoppaper and assignedpaper.
ekaw#Negative_Review: The negativereview is the child of review and the parent of the neutralreview.
ekaw#Review: Review is a child of the program brochure. It is the parent of the positivereview and the neutralreview.
ekaw#Neutral_Review: neutralreview is a child of review and is the parent of negativereview.
ekaw#Organising_Agency: organisingagency is a child of the organisation which is parented by proceedingspublisher.
ekaw#Academic_Institution: The academicinstitution is the child of the organisation which is parented by the proceedingspublisher and the researchinstitute. The university is also the parent of the academicinstitution.
ekaw#Organisation: The parent organisation of proceedingspublisher is the organisingagency. The academicinstitution is the parent organisation of researchinstitute.
ekaw#Proceedings_Publisher: The proceedingspublisher is a child of the organisation which is parented by the academicinstitution.
ekaw#Poster_Paper: The posterpaper is a child of paper which is the parent of the website.
ekaw#Regular_Paper: The regularpaper is a child of paper which is the parent of the website.
ekaw#Demo_Paper: Demopaper is a child of paper which is the parent of industrialpaper.
ekaw#Research_Institute: The researchinstitute is child of the academicinstitution which is parented by the proceedingspublisher.
ekaw#Scientific_Event: The event scientificevent is the parent of both conferencetrip and workshop. It is also the parent of contributedtalk and is the parent of the event socialvent.
ekaw#Invited_Talk_Abstract: invitedtalkabstract is the child of abstract and is the parent of tutorialabstract.
ekaw#Agency_Staff_Member: The agency staff member is the child of the conference participant and the parent of the conference participant.
ekaw#Workshop_Session: The workshopsession is a child of the scientificevent which is also a child of the event.
ekaw#Track: The track is a child of scientificevent which is a parent of socialevent.
ekaw#Invited_Talk: invitedtalk is a child of individualpresentation which is a child of scientificevent.
ekaw#Workshop: The workshop is child of scientificevent which is parented by socialvent which is parented by conferencetrip.
ekaw#Tutorial: The tutorial is child of individualpresentation which is parented by contributedtalk.
ekaw#Contributed_Talk: Contributedtalk is a child of individualpresentation which is parented by a tutorial.
ekaw#Conference: The conference is the child of the scientificevent which is the parent of the session and the demosession.
ekaw#Demo_Chair: The demochair is the child of the conferenceparticipant and the parent of the agency staff member.
ekaw#Tutorial_Chair: The pcmember is the parent of the sessionchair who is the child of the conferenceparticipant and the child of the conferenceparticipant.
ekaw#PC_Chair: pcchair is the child of conferenceparticipant and paperauthor. pcmember is the child of possiblereviewer and pcmember is the child of pcmember.
ekaw#PC_Member: pcchair is the parent of scmember and sessionchair. pcchair is the parent of conferenceparticipant and paperauthor. pcchair is the parent of scmember and workshopchair.
ekaw#OC_Member: ocmember is the parent of occhair and is the child of a conferenceparticipant who is a lateregistered participant.
ekaw#Proceedings: The conferenceproceedings is the parent of the proceedings which are the child of the multiauthorvolume.
ekaw#Programme_Brochure: The programmebrochure is a child of document which is parented by paper which is also parented by cameraready paper.
ekaw#Flyer: The flyer is a child of document which is parented by the conferenceproceedings and the multiauthorvolume.
ekaw#Web_Site: The website is the child of the document review which is the parent of positivereview.
ekaw#Multi-author_Volume: The multiauthorvolume is the parent of proceedings, conferenceproceedings and review. The review is the parent of neutralreview.
ekaw#Individual_Presentation: Individualpresentation is the parent of contributedtalk and invitedtalk. It is also the child of scientificevent and conference.
ekaw#OC_Chair: occhair is a child of ocmember who is a conference participant.
ekaw#Conference_Banquet: The conferencebanquet is a child of socialvent which is a child of an event.
ekaw#Workshop_Chair: The workshopchair is the child of the conferenceparticipant and the parent of the tutorialchair. The pcmember is also the child of the workshopchair.
ekaw#Conference_Proceedings: The conferenceproceedings is the child of the proceedings, the multiauthor volume is the child of the abstract and the invitedtalkabstract.
ekaw#Session_Chair: The sessionchair is the child of the conferenceparticipant and the parent of the pcchair.
ekaw#Early-Registered_Participant: The earlyregisteredparticipant is the child of the conferenceparticipant who is the parent of ocmember and occhair.
ekaw#Late-Registered_Participant: The lateregisteredparticipant is a child of the conferenceparticipant and the parent of the tutorialchair. pcmember and scmember are both children of the tutorialchair.
ekaw#University: The university is the child of the academicinstitution which is the parent of the researchinstitute.
ekaw#Possible_Reviewer: The possiblereviewer is a child of the person who is the parent of the agency staff member and the parent of the sessionchair.
ekaw#Student: The student is the child of the person who is the parent of the paperauthor.
ekaw#Invited_Speaker: The invited speaker is the child of the presenter and the conferenceparticipant. The sessionchair is the child of the pcmember and the conferenceparticipant is the parent of the sessionchair.
ekaw#Presenter: The presenter is a child of the conferenceparticipant who is the parent of the earlyregistered participant and the invited speaker.
ekaw#SC_Member: scmember is a child of pcmember who is the parent of sessionchair. The conferenceparticipant is a child of the conferenceparticipant.
